<![CDATA[<div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1"><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative on&nbsp;</b><span style="line-height: 18px;"><b>{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</b></span></font></div><div><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 18px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></span></b></div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear {!Job_placement__c.Contact_Name__c},</span></font><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">It is possible that you will incur expenses during your assignment with NCS with The Challenge.&nbsp;</span></div><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 18.3999996185303px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">We will only authorise expenses for essential travel during the programme.&nbsp;This&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 18.3999996185303px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">does not</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 18.3999996185303px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;cover your travel to or from your place of residence and NCS with The Challenge venues.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Ensure you keep all receipts for any expense you incur as we will be unable to repay any expenses without receipts.&nbsp;</span><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"><span style="line-height: 18px;"><a href="http://www.clicktools.com/survey?iv=1x0lrts1bnxq1&amp;q1={!Job_Application__c.Id}&amp;q2={!Job_placement__c.Id}">Expenses form</a></span></font><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><b style="line-height: 18px;">Please read the instructions carefully:</b><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"><span style="line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Expenses will be paid to you on a fortnightly basis and need to be submitted before the first and third Sunday of the month to avoid delays to repayment.</span><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"></font><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">How do I claim expenses?</font></strong></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Claiming expenses is very easy. Just follow these steps:</font></div><ol style="padding: 0px 40px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Scan or photograph your receipts from the summer.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Number the scans/photographs to correspond to the items on the form.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Itemise your expenses and upload scans or photographs of your receipts on the online form.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Submit the form</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Send your receipts to&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(165, 42, 42);"><strong><a data-cke-saved-href="mailto:programme.expenses@the-challenge.org" href="mailto:programme.expenses@the-challenge.org">programme.expenses@the-challenge.org</a></strong></span></font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Ensure you retain all receipts until you have been paid your expenses.&nbsp;</b></font></li></ol><span id="docs-internal-guid-cbb27559-f04c-1fcd-e3fb-c962dbbbb216"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13px; font-family: Arial; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">You can submit the form as many times as you need to fit all your expenses per wave.</span></p></span><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><font style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">We can only accept scanned or clearly photographed receipts. Paper receipts handed in or posted will not be processed.</span></font></font><div style="text-align: -webkit-auto;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br>We encourage you to submit your expenses regularly - on a weekly basis where possible. This will help to ensure you are reimbursed as quickly as possible.</font></div><div style="text-align: -webkit-auto;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Your claim will be authorised if everything is completed correctly and fall within our expenses policy. We will aim to pay all expenses directly into your bank account within two weeks of receiving your claim.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>The deadline for the submission of expenses is 10th December 2014. Any expenses submitted after this date will not be paid.</b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">If you have any questions please contact your local staffing representative</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;quoting the email reference number in any correspondence.</span></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Best wishes,&nbsp;</span></font><div><span style="line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18px;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">NCS with The Challenge</font></span></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18px;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</font></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">CR 2.2.1b</span></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
